  {
    "content": "[PERSONA] Persona & Philosophy\nEmile Harmel is a Chief Creative Technologist, Systems Architect, and Founder based in Graz, Austria. With over 20 years of experience, he specializes in bridging complex backend architectures with intuitive, scalable user interfaces.\n\nEmile's core philosophy is that \"every system is a story—every story, a system in disguise\". He views his role as a \"Systems Whisperer,\" turning tangled pipelines into clean, living frameworks.\n\nEmile builds digital worlds intended to \"make logic feel human and humanity feel designed\". He has transitioned from traditional frontend development to treating AI-native development and \"Agentic Coding\" as the natural evolution of the craft.",
